text: Scottish actress best known for her role as Margaret Thompson in Boardwalk Empire (2010-2014). She had also appeared in films such as Nanny McPhee (2005), Gosford Park (2001), and as the voice of Merida in Brave (2012). ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Glasgow Category:Emmy Award winning actors Category:Scottish movie actors Category:Screen Actors Guild Award winners
